+qdrant_added: false
+llm_or_openvino_added: false
+search_commands_bounded: n/a
+```
+
+## Guardrails
+
+```text
+No CLI.
+No daemon.
+No OpenRC service.
+No resident watcher.
+No runtime code.
+No Scheduler.run() modification.
+No PriorityQueue modification.
+No Dispatcher implementation modification.
+No PolicyEngine implementation modification.
